sed on the premium between perpetual and mark prices, with payments occurring every hour at minute zero. The exchange uses a TWAP mechanism over the funding interval to determine rates, typically ranging from -0.375% to +0.375% per payment. Bluefin's order book model and institutional matching engine ensure accurate price discovery, while Sui's sub-second finality enables rapid position adjustments for funding rate arbitrage."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
